description: NP3 Fastigheter AB engages in the ownership and management of industrial, commercial, logistics, and office properties. The company is headquartered in Sundsvall, Vasternorrland and currently employs 46 full-time employees. The company went IPO on 2014-12-04. The Company’s business concept is to acquire properties for tenants with a focus on commercial premises in locations outside city centers. The company mainly offers properties within the categories industrial, logistics and offices. Its business activities are entirely conducted in Northern Sweden and comprise markets, such as Umea, Dalarna, Sundsvall and Gaevle, among others.
